						<p><hi rend="italic">Village gate-way near the Chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">A.D. 1755.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record in Nāgarī characters is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1677, Yuva, Chaitra śu. Pratīpadā,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1755, March 13, Thursday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records in Mārāṭhi, the construction of a gate in the village <hi rend="bold">Bījaragi.</hi></p>						

